{"tid":1612619,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"國父孫文遺囑","createTime":"2019-10-02T10:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T17:22:48.000Z","uid":75277,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6590039c023d4c97f8423b5c323fb9fae52e31df","tid":1612619,"uid":75277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"余致力國民革命，凡四十年，其目的在求中國之自由平等。積四十年之經驗，深知欲達到此目的，<span style=\"color: red;\">必須喚起民眾及聯合世界上以平等待我之民族，共同奮鬥</span>。<br />\n<br />\n現在革命尚未成功，凡我同志，務須依照余所著《建國方略》、《建國大綱》、《三民主義》及《第一次全國代表大會宣言》，繼續努力，以求貫徹。最近主張開國民會議及廢除不平等條約，尤須於最短期間，促其實現。是所至囑！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/98/Will_of_premier_1925.jpg/1920px-Will_of_premier_1925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F9%2F98%2FWill_of_premier_1925.jpg%2F1920px-Will_of_premier_1925.jpg&h=bc7e762a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中華民國十四年二月二十四日<br />\n孫文 三月十一日補簽<br />\n筆記者 汪精衛<br />\n證明者 宋子文<br />\n孫科<br />\n孔祥熙<br />\n邵元沖 戴恩賽<br />\n吳敬恆 何香凝<br />\n戴季陶 鄒魯"},{"pid":"3c0aa5d42f1763607122e655f4518f1258332edf","tid":1612619,"uid":69646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f75e8b5159968076e3648c8695be736b184cf419","tid":1612619,"uid":75277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fdc2ddd7cffac96cc2b104a508c9873194a393","tid":1612619,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"三民主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12e933d02ae3f1e685b0683fb9f02aab3be69f4","tid":1612619,"uid":36134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"條友聯俄容共<br />\n又推行蘇聯一黨專政 黨領導軍隊咁既模式<br />\n毛魔都話好多野係師